116
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:01,920
No!

117
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:09,920
The cherries look nice.

118
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,280
Take it easy!

119
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,680
You can't even wash my feet!

120
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,920
You're useless!

121
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,200
You see him as your husband,

122
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,880
but you're just a free caretaker to him.

123
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:44,640
Li Xiaolian.

124
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,040
Are you out of your mind?

125
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,320
Yes!

126
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:49,400
You will pay for my service every day!

127
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,240
Otherwise,

128
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,640
I'll never serve you for free!

129
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,200
Xiaolian!

130
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,400
You...

